995
00:48:20,480 --> 00:48:22,679
[SPEAKER_03] Dakle, ne to, pa onda ovo.

996
00:48:22,679 --> 00:48:23,300
[SPEAKER_03] To je opasno.

997
00:48:23,300 --> 00:48:23,699
[SPEAKER_03] To nije.

998
00:48:23,699 --> 00:48:24,539
[SPEAKER_03] To je magija.

999
00:48:24,539 --> 00:48:33,699
[SPEAKER_03] Obrati se, ružo.

1000
00:48:33,699 --> 00:48:34,300
[SPEAKER_03] Nema drugog.

1001
00:48:34,300 --> 00:48:35,920
[SPEAKER_03] Dobro.

1002
