1006
00:48:45,139 --> 00:48:46,199
[SPEAKER_03] Ima neko ko pati?

1007
00:48:46,199 --> 00:48:47,739
[SPEAKER_03] Je li ima neki tvoj prijatelj

1008
00:48:47,739 --> 00:48:50,719
